<HEADLINE> Top PLA Officer on Army Building (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The stationing of PLA troops in Hong Kong is an important
symbol of China's resumed exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong
as well as a special and great mission for the PLA, he said. At
present, preparations in various fields have been under way in a
planned and systematic way, he said.
</P>
<P>
The PLA will bear in mind the important entrustment of the
motherland as well as the purpose of the PLA after it stations
troops in Hong Kong. It will also maintain the true political
qualities of the army and give its excellent tradition into full
play, he said.
</P>
<P>
He called on PLA soldiers to be stationed in Hong Kong to
respect the Hong Kong government, love Hong Kong compatriots and
abide by laws of the state and military regulations.
</P>
<P>
He also called on them to abide by laws in the Hong Kong
Special Administrative Region (HKSAR), especially the Basic Law of
the HKSAR and Law on Stationing Troop in HKSAR. They should stand
up to tests in whatever complicated situations to contribute to
Hong Kong's long-term prosperity and stability.
</P>
<P>
"The officers and rank-and-file of the whole army will
steadfastly safeguard the authority of the Party Central Committee
with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core," said Liu, noting that "this
is the political wish of Comrade Deng Xiaoping when he was living
as well as a requirement of the party, the people and the
socialist cause," he said.
</P>
<P>
