<P>
He said that CRIF will not "fall in the trap" prepared by Le
Pen, who he said always produces a media scandal and then claims
himself the victim of it.
</P>
<P>
Hajdenberg also said that he is "determined to see the justice
condemn Jean-Marie Le Pen for his anti-Semitist declarations on
the Jewish conspiracy."
</P>
<P>
