</P>
<P>
During his stay here, Arafat briefed Egyptian President Hosni
Mubarak on the latest developments of conditions in the occupied
Palestinian territories, including the effects of Israel's recent
decision to set up a new Jewish neighborhood in Jerusalem on the
peace process.
