"Hong Kong People governing Hong Kong" and a high degree of
autonomy will ensure a better future for Hong Kong after July 1,
1997. The Chinese daily also commented on the reform of the
state-owned enterprises, which will top the agenda of economic
restructuring this year. "It shows that the Chinese government has
made great determination to solve the problems concerning
state-owned business," said the paper.
</P>
